{
  "stem": "11184.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- the German, the Nazi, called each-- each compartment to see where my mother is so I could be with her together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you're talking about wagons and compartments, are they-- are you talking about the train already?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or were these the carts taking them to the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was already at the train station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what I was gonna say-- I'm-- I'm mixing a little up now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm mixing a little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened is that-- that-- that a girl asked me to go, and I did not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my little ration card and mother's was taken away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we did not come at that time to the place to be taken away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they did not feed us at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was before.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, this was with--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when the friend--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my friend, when she begged me to go with her-- right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- and my intuition said no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're not going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was hiding for two weeks-- mother and me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mother went at night somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went somewhere else, you know, wherever we could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- because the Jewish police was looking for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, they had your names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and I told her, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, she did go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after the war, I found out where they were taken-- to Chelmno.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was-- everybody was finished up there-- finished off there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my intuition said no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the last day I couldn't anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Almost, I almost was ready to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of the sudden, I hear voices in the streets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People are so happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They stopped the selections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They are not taking people out anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was great.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what happened, they decided to take everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They decided to close the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
